skins.shipDescription: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri! Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon! Ay have come from the great beyond with my accompanying spirits!
skins.selfIntroduction: What an unexpected joy that this place allows me to brandish all my power! Were I to take my blades, Rasetsu and Asura, and unsheathe them¡­
skins.acquisition: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri! Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon! Ay have come from the great beyond with my accompanying spirits!
skins.login: Ay must deepen my bond with humanity now after my arrival in this world! And you must watch my stream today!
skins.details: It appears there is another who goes by the name of "demon" here. It is my hope to meet with them!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Does all of humanity view you as a celebrated individual, Commander?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Don't gaze upon me so intently!
skins.secretaryIdle3: With you and your followers for company, of course Ay am not lonely!
skins.secretaryTouch: Hm? My swords? The red one is Asura, and this is Rakshasa. Aren't they cool?
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: Some believe my surname "Nakiri" originates from the phrase "cut the hand that pats"... Surely you wishn't to find out if that is truly the case, Commander?
skins.secretaryHeadpat: Do not touch my horns on a whim!

skins.shipDescription: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!
skins.acquisition: Be cheery, for here's Nakiri~! Ay am not used to this outfit and am a little embarrassed... But Ay am Nakiri Ayame, Hololive's virtual demon!
skins.login: Ay have waited for you! The ocean floor is where our next battlefield lies!
skins.details: Ay am afraid to swing my swords around looking like this... so Ay shall fight with you using my will-o'-wisps!
skins.secretaryIdle1: Umm, Commander? Would you not stare at me so much?
skins.secretaryIdle2: Many say Ay am easily amused, but that doesn't... Pfft, ahahahahah! Commander! Don't expressly try to make me laugh like this! Hahahahah!
skins.secretaryIdle3: My appearance may have changed, but my skill in battle has not!
skins.secretaryTouch: Tis a swimsuit with a cute design and feel, you say? Quite so, quite so~ More praise wouldn't be undue!
